  "response_text": "A bright, tidy bathroom comes into view, painted in pale blue-green tones. In the foreground, the white toilet tank fills the left side of the scene, with a shiny chrome flush handle on its front. Three small blue animated Scrubbing Bubbles characters sit on top of the tank like little domed brushes, each with a round blue body, expressive eyes, a smiling mouth, and tan bristles underneath. In the background, a young adult man with light skin, dark hair, a short-sleeved blue button-up shirt, and dark pants steps into the bathroom doorway. He pauses, looking toward the toilet and the little blue characters, then smiles with a slightly amused, reluctant expression.\n\nThe view moves closer to the three blue characters on the toilet tank. They face one another and the room, their eyes shifting and mouths changing as if they are speaking. One turns partly away, another looks surprised, and the third smiles calmly, making them appear like a small team ready to handle the job.\n\nA hand then holds a blue cylindrical applicator inside the open white toilet bowl. The applicator has a pale translucent end pressed against the inner side of the bowl just under the rim. As the hand pushes and twists or presses, a small turquoise-blue gel disc is left sticking to the porcelain. The applicator is pulled away, leaving the gel spot in place. A small “dramatisation” note appears faintly near the lower left of these demonstration images. Close beside the gel, grey words appear on the inside of the bowl reading “LIMESCALE” and “HARD WATER,” visually indicating the kinds of buildup the gel is meant to work against.\n\nBack at the toilet, the three blue Scrubbing Bubbles characters sit on the tank lid again. The white toilet seat is up in the foreground, partially blocking the right side of the view. The characters look around and at each other with satisfied, playful expressions, as though reacting to the cleaned or protected toilet. Their eyes move toward the raised seat, and their faces shift from pleased to mildly pointed or expectant.\n\nThe final image presents the product clearly on a white bathroom surface. A blue Scrubbing Bubbles Toilet Cleaning Gel applicator lies on its side next to a green-and-blue product box labeled “Scrubbing Bubbles Toilet Cleaning Gel,” with the Scrubbing Bubbles logo and an image of the gel being applied inside a toilet bowl. Large white text on the wall behind the product reads, “WE WORK HARD SO YOU DON’T HAVE TO.” In the background, the toilet remains visible with the seat raised, keeping the bathroom setting and product use connected.",
